  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with 2000-2004 Audi A6 Quattro with 2.7L Turbocharged</li>\n<li>Compatible with 2001-2005 Audi Allroad Quattro with 2.7L Turbocharged</li>\n<li>Compatible with 2000-2002 Audi S4 with 2.7L Turbocharged</li>\n<li>Compatible with 2002 Audi RS4 with 2.7L Turbocharged</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Designed to fit directly on the OEM exhaust system</li>\n<li>Upgrading on the K04 turbos on the S4 requires these new turbo inlet pipes from the RS4</li>\n<li>Connects to the larger turbo inlet and makes the turbos a direct bolt-on application</li>\n<li>Increased BHP, more efficient airflow from turbo, improved throttle response</li>\n<li>CNC machined to the highest standards from 6061 aluminum</li>\n<li>Actuator has a high-temp silicone Nomex-reinforced diaphragm for extended life</li>\n<li>100% brand new items, never used or installed</li>\n<li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n<li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Package Includes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>4× inlet pipes</li>\n<li>4× silicon elbow (blue)</li>\n<li>4× T-bolt clamps</li>\n<li>All necessary gaskets and O-rings (as shown in pictures)</li>\n</ul>",
